properties.abstract: The mountain village of Stoos is situated on a small plateau high above the Schwyz basin. Up here there is a short but interesting and varied bike tour with the most fantastic views.
properties.description:
The top station of the Schwyz/Schlattli-Stoos funicular is the departure point for a short bike tour in the car-free village of Stoos. As the tour does not lead into the high Alps, it can be done as early as spring without the risk of having to cross snow fields. Unlike the longer Fronalp tour, it offers even less experienced mountain bikers the opportunity of exploring the wonderful mountain world of Central Switzerland by bike.

In Stoos there are numerous places offering refreshments ranging from rustic, traditional restaurants to mini supermarket. The short tour is ideally combined with a trip on the chairlift to the Fronalpstock.
properties.name: Stoos-Muotatal Tourismus
properties.title: Stoos Tour
